attributes.Long form description: The student looks at the table and sees that it needs a repair. The student gets to work and screws the first leg of the shelf into place. The student continues working and screws all four legs of the table into place. The student finishes by putting the table on the top. The student looks at the hex socket heads to make sure they are in place.
